author: Christine Schreyer -- Kala Kaŋa Bi ŋa Kapia
notes: Taken from data compiled by Christine Schreyer, Chara DeVolder, and John Wagner in all six villages of Kala speakers along the Huon Gulf 2010-2013. <l> represents /ɾ/ and <y> = /j/.
problems: Some words I have collected during fieldwork but have not yet published, so I have not included those.
